snippet.textDisplay: So after watching this video the bottom line is Apple is launching nothing new or ground breaking in 2020. Love the logic of 'Why would you have a 108|MP camera when 64MP is good enough'! Apple is clearly playing catch-up and offering customers minimum specs at highest margins. A 10% battery increase is welcome but far from where the competition is now and some offer OLED, high spec camera, 5G, bigger screens and batteries for half the cost of an iPhone. It's the low end and cheaper older iPhones that have been keeping their market share up everywhere outside the USA so the basic iPhone might prove to be the big hit in 2020 for those that value branding above performance.
snippet.textOriginal: So after watching this video the bottom line is Apple is launching nothing new or ground breaking in 2020. Love the logic of 'Why would you have a 108|MP camera when 64MP is good enough'! Apple is clearly playing catch-up and offering customers minimum specs at highest margins. A 10% battery increase is welcome but far from where the competition is now and some offer OLED, high spec camera, 5G, bigger screens and batteries for half the cost of an iPhone. It's the low end and cheaper older iPhones that have been keeping their market share up everywhere outside the USA so the basic iPhone might prove to be the big hit in 2020 for those that value branding above performance.
